      • How to connect with the smart watch？

        1.Search “FitCloundPro” on Google Play or APP Store or scan the QR code to download.

        2.Open the "FitCloundPro" APP,click the "+ Add Peripheral Now" button on the "Devices" screen.

        3.Tap "K65PRO" to pair.

      • How do I turn off the Medio Audio?

        When the smartwatch and phone are connected by Bluetooth, the smartwatch may sync the phone audio. If you want to keep it quiet,you can tap the phone icon to turn off the “media audio“.

      • What if the strap dimensions don't fit my wrist ?

        1.The product comes with a strap regulator, which can be adjusted according to your wrist.

        2.If you need a longer strap, we can provide you with extra strap sections.

      • How to use bluetooth voice call?

        1.Make sure your smartwatch is connected to your mobile phone by Bluetooth.

        2.Swipe down the smartwatch screen and tap the "Call" icon.

        3.Open the “phone" function in the app.
